headline: Amcor to Report First Quarter 2026 Results
summary: Amcor plc (NYSE: AMCR; ASX: AMC) will announce its First Quarter 2026 results for the three months ended 30 September 2025 after the US market closes on Wednesday 5 November 2025.

headline: How Recent Developments Are Rewriting the Story for Amcor
summary: Amcor’s consensus analyst price target was recently trimmed from $10.59 to $10.43 per share, a small but notable reduction. The adjustment comes as analysts weigh both the opportunities and risks following Amcor’s acquisition of Berry Global, balancing optimism about synergies with caution regarding integration and sector headwinds.
